Lesson 2.5 - Game theory of health

---------- [L1]

RSS feed link: https://rss.com/podcasts/footnerdprogram/397561

Video link: https://youtu.be/miMgXlLWXps

Creators: Nick & Ruth

Framework:

- what is game theory?
- outcomes follow incentives
- sickcare system
- mis-aligned incentives
- creating a new health system with aligned incentives
- legacy medicine

Audio lesson notes:
- detailed notes and timestamps from the audio lesson


Experiments

- Explain the concept of game theory to someone
- Write down 2 good experiences and 2 negative experiences you have personally had with medicine in your life
- What are 3 ways we can incentivize health as a society?
- Does medicine enhance or degrade health? Explain your perspective
- Write down ideas about how we can align health provider compensation with positive health outcomes

